@NODE Installation "ImageEditor - Installation"

@{PAR}@{JCENTER}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{B}If you wan't to see what you are working on,@{LINE}
you urgently need a good@{FG TEXT} pbm.datatype!@{UB}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{JCENTER}pbm.datatype @{B}43.10@{UB} (1997), © 1995/97 by Matthias Scheler@{LINE}
pbm.datatype @{B}44.2@{UB} (21.03.1999), © 1998/99 by Gunther Nikl@{LINE}
@{FG HIGHLIGHT}gnikl\@informatik.uni-rostock.de@{FG TEXT} - @{FG HIGHLIGHT}http://home.pages.de/~munk/@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}
@{JLEFT}
@{LINDENT 4}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Archives to download@{UB}@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 8}@{LINE}
The Amiga NetPBM binaries are available from: <ftp://ftp.informatik.uni-oldenburg.de>@{LINE}
AmiNet will probably carry them too, look under:@{LINE}@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/pbmbin.lha> @{B}Bitmap@{UB}-Filter@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/pgmbin.lha> @{B}Graymap@{UB}-Filter@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/ppmbin1.lha> @{B}Pixmap@{UB}-Filter I@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/ppmbin2.lha> @{B}Pixmap@{UB}-Filter II@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/pnmbin.lha> @{B}Anymap@{UB}-Filter@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/netpbmwos.lha> @{B}PPC WarpOS@{UB}-Filter@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/dttoppm.lha> @{B}Loader@{UB} [dttoppm]@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/ilbmtoppm.lha> @{B}Loader@{UB} [ilbmtoppm]@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/pnmtoljpg.lha> @{B}Saver@{UB} [pnmtoljpg]@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/gfx/pbm/pnmtopng.lha> @{B}Saver@{UB} [pnmtopng]@{LINE}
