@{LINDENT 4}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Archive to download@{UB} @{I}(...for ImageIcons only) @{UI}@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 8}@{LINE}
AmiNet will probably carry it under:@{LINE}@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/util/wb/Image2Icon.lha>@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 4}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Archive to download@{UB} @{I}(...for HTML Online-Help only) @{UI}@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 8}@{LINE}
AmiNet will probably carry it under:@{LINE}@{LINE}
<http://de.aminet.net/aminet/aminet/util/dtype/html-dt.lzx>@{LINE}
