@NODE Requirements "ImageEditor - Requirements"

@{LINDENT 4}
@{PAR}@{B}Operating System@{UB}@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 8}@{LINE}
Make sure that your Operating System is of the Version @{B}39.x@{UB} or higher.
You also need the Workbench Version @{B}39.x@{UB}.@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 4}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Memory@{UB}@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 8}@{LINE}
You defintily need a minimum of @{B}2000.000 bytes@{UB} of Memory to run this program.
@{B}CHIP@{UB}-Ram and @{B}FAST@{UB}-Ram are usable.
You also need a lot of Disk-Memory, because the whole program based on a concept of primary using IO-Streams.
If you have more than @{B}16 Mbytes@{UB} of Memory, you coul'd speed up every operation using the Ram-Disk as a temporay workplace.
If not, use "Addbuffers" to speed up a little bit.@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 4}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Libraries@{UB}@{LINE}
@{LINDENT 8}@{LINE}
Make sure that the following libraries are found in the logical device path @{B}libs:@{UB}.@{LINE}
@{LINE}
ą libs:@{B}cando.library@{UB} (Version @{B}3.003@{UB} or higher)@{LINE}
@{TAB}@{TAB}...or...@{LINE}
ą PROGDIR:libs/@{B}cando.library@{UB}@{LINE}
@{LINE}
˛ libs:@{B}amigaguide.library@{UB} (Version @{B}39.0@{UB} or higher)@{LINE}
˛ libs:@{B}asl.library@{UB} (Version @{B}38.3@{UB} or higher)@{LINE}
˛ libs:@{B}datatype.library@{UB} (Version @{B}39.7@{UB} or higher)@{LINE}
@{LINE}
ł libs:@{B}reqtools.library@{UB} (Version @{B}38.1200@{UB} or higher)@{LINE}
@{LINE}
